# Project Scaffolding

## Where things go

| What | Where | Example |
|------|-------|---------|
| Quant math, signals, models | `core/{submodule}/` | `core/signals/mean_reversion.py` |
| Pydantic schemas | `api/schemas/` | `api/schemas/backtest.py` |
| API route handlers | `api/routes/` | `api/routes/momentum.py` |
| React pages | `frontend/src/pages/` | `ManualPortfolioBuilder.tsx` |
| Reusable UI components | `frontend/src/components/{category}/` | `components/charts/EquityCurve.tsx` |
| TypeScript types + API client | `frontend/src/lib/` | `lib/types.ts`, `lib/api.ts` |
| Data scripts (ETL, backfill) | `scripts/` | `scripts/update_daily.py` |
| Tests | `tests/` | `tests/test_metrics_risk.py` |
| Exploration | `notebooks/` | `notebooks/09_vol_surface.ipynb` |
| Config and environment | `config/` | `config/settings.py` |
| Feature docs | `docs/` | `docs/PLATFORM_STATUS.md` |

## Dependency direction (never violate)

```
frontend → api (HTTP only, never Python imports)
api/routes → core (Python imports, thin delegation)
core → (no upward imports to api or frontend)
scripts → core + config (standalone CLI)
tests → core + api (test both layers)
notebooks → core (import, never copy-paste logic)
```

## Adding a new strategy (checklist)

1. `core/` — implement logic + add tests in `tests/`
2. `core/strategies/registry.py` — register `StrategyMetadata`
3. `api/schemas/` — request/response Pydantic models
4. `api/routes/` — thin handler, register router in `api/main.py`
5. `frontend/src/lib/types.ts` — TypeScript interfaces
6. `frontend/src/lib/api.ts` — client method
7. `frontend/src/pages/` — page component with `AppLayout`
8. `App.tsx` — add route; `TopBar.tsx` — add nav link

## Adding a new frontend page (checklist)

1. Create `frontend/src/pages/MyPage.tsx` using `AppLayout` slots
2. Add types in `lib/types.ts`, API methods in `lib/api.ts`
3. Import in `App.tsx`, add `<Route>`
4. Add nav link in `components/layout/TopBar.tsx`
